dual-prohibition-khamr\/","url_meta":{"origin":24901,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Alcohol: Gradual prohibition of wine, intoxicants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn Shurahbil reported: When the prohibition of wine was yet to be declared, Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Allah, give us a clear explanation of wine.\u201d Allah revealed the verse, \u201cThey ask you about wine and gambling. Say: In them is great sin,\u201d (2:219). Umar was called and it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3123,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/04\/haram-khamr-carrion-pork\/","url_meta":{"origin":24901,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Harm: Allah forbids alcohol, carrion, pork","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has forbidden wine and its sale. He has forbidden carrion and its sale. He has forbidden swine and its sale.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3485 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8643,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/22\/khamr-by-other-names\/","url_meta":{"